i/JDocFile/TPDV/111%2c%e5%8b%9e%e5%b0%88%e8%aa%bf%2c256%2c20220912%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDV,111,勞專調,256,20220912,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"勞專調","JNO":"256","JDATE":"20220912","JTITLE":"損害賠償"}